    <title>奥特曼500系列软胶</title>
    <link href="http://bemura.github.io/2020/07/02/%E5%A5%A5%E7%89%B9%E6%9B%BC500%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E8%BD%AF%E8%83%B6/"/>
    <id>http://bemura.github.io/2020/07/02/%E5%A5%A5%E7%89%B9%E6%9B%BC500%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E8%BD%AF%E8%83%B6/</id>
    <published>2020-07-02T04:52:48.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-08-30T14:17:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/08/29/vFPDzbV5OTHfsGK.png" title="">    <br></center><p>淘宝买的玩具到货，拍张照纪念一下，以后新买的怪兽玩具就发在这里好了</p><p>泽塔新怪兽做工不错，赛文加的银色喷漆很好看，可惜500系软胶的尺寸都是14厘米高，放在以前买的17厘米软胶边上就像小朋友</p><p>7月中旬乌英达姆差不多就要发售了，到时候再买几个</p><center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/07/02/twEWAQMPmkH7IRB.jpg" title="セブンガー">    <br>    <div style="color:orange;    display: inline-block;;    color: #999;    padding: 10px;">特空机一号 赛文加</div></center><center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/07/02/NlazjE4eGKxMBfq.jpg" title="ゲネガーグ">    <br>    <div style="color:orange;     display: inline-block;    color: #999;    padding: 10px;">凶暴宇宙鲛 盖内伽古</div></center><p>趁乌英达姆发售另买了赛文第14&amp;15集登场的金古桥和初代第39集登场的杰顿</p><center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/07/20/Nzskom7RPSOEnV8.jpg" title="キングジョー">    <br>    <div style="color:orange;    display: inline-block;;    color: #999;    padding: 10px;">宇宙机器人 金古桥</div></center><p>（金古桥左脚有点变形，用U盘垫了一下）</p><center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/07/20/Ps6K5Cd7MQhop4I.jpg" title="ゼットン">    <br>    <div style="color:orange;    display: inline-block;;    color: #999;    padding: 10px;">宇宙恐龙 杰顿</div></center><center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/07/20/4itfVxlEDSYuWba.jpg" title="ウインダム">    <br>    <div style="color:orange;    display: inline-block;;    color: #999;    padding: 10px;">特空机二号 乌英达姆</div></center>]]></content>
    
