    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<center>    <img style="border-radius: 0.5125em;    box-shadow: 0 2px 4px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.12),0 2px 10px 0 rgba(34,36,38,.08);"    src="https://i.loli.net/2020/08/29/xtlAFBDKogiXhLc.png" title="">    <br></center><p>听说Hexo自建博客连服务器都不用，就试着搞了一个</p><p>虽然页面主题不够简洁，但比WordPress上的傻瓜博客干净多了</p><p>博客搞起来很简单，没出啥问题，参考了<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这</a><a href="https://medium.com/@bebebobohaha/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-hexo-gitpage-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA-blog-5c6ed52f23db" target="_blank" rel="noopener">三</a><a href="https://medium.com/@z0935323866/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%9E%B6%E8%A8%ADhexo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-7074161158f8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">篇</a>教程</p><p>接下来完善一下About页面</p>]]></content>
    
